Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know this one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can solve them so easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... going at it, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work, Higurashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perfect score!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Getting into high school is a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is NOT a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a dream, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Going back home again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know how much trouble that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, but I have an important exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Exam"?\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An examination... another word for test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not another"test"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really need to review.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things are so complicated for Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'd be easier if she just\nstayed here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you like"test" that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:24.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'd like three days or so\nto go back to my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Back to your village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean to the Demon Slayer's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... I want to repair my\NHiraikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've used it an awful lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang it! Only three days then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! That means I can go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry about this. I'll return to Kaede's\nin three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess we get to take\nit easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Sango's here,\nyou can't take it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Err... I didn't mean\nit like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha agreed so readily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This should be safe enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After I made you an apprentice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sneaking away from training!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were suffering from\nexposure and hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you were forced to fight\nin the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you didn't want to die\nlike a worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were the very one who\nsaid that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,F-Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were sick of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I agreed to bring you\nhere to Togenkyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to train to become a sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget about becoming a sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had enough of\nthis frightening place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a heavy fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a creepy-looking fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a... human-faced fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human-faced fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Using humans as nourishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a demon tree bears Ninmenka, fruits\nwith human faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tree of the\NHuman-faced Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:32.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But so many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,must mean that the tree is\nextremely large.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! This is the Warring Age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there's a battle, there's no shortage\nof dead bodies forfertilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would there be a battle so\ndeep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay then! Let's go investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Weren't you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:00.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd be too worried to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And besides, the test is in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget about taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!\NDon't just ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop dawdling!\NI'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's take care of\nthis business quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon tree is probably\nup there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Above this cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:48.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a\ncolossal human-faced fruit tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this demonic aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:56.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means its consumed quite a\nlot of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna chop down that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sun would set if I had to haul\neach of you up this cliff, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha intends to deal with it\nbefore the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the first of the lunar month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lunar month?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The night of the new moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The night that Inuyasha loses\nhis powers and becomes a mortal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why Inuyasha was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! No Fruit of Longevity yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eating this is becoming boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who planted this demon tree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph... what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn... I don't pick up any\ndemonic scent from him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he reeks of dead men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't gonna waste time talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm gonna chop down that\ncreepy tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay away, otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:24.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll chop you up as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why that... flabby punk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga doesn't work on him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go with the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Wind Scar doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know where you're from,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but did you think\nyou could defeat a sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... I am the Sage of Togenkyo-\NTokajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The gourd is getting bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're shrinking's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Tetsusaiga is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! It's no illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you r-really a sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop making me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're truly a sage,\nwhy'd you stoop to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This demon will make\nnice fertilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Shippo!\NJust a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're quite strong, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd forgotten all about it...\NThat tonight was a new moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the sun sets,\NInuyasha will turn human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:10.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems like someone lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:30.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What IS this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do they live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel Shards are\ngrowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The box garden is getting bigger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:00.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not it... We're shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:17.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are the tiny men who\nwere walking around earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're in the box garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!\NWhat'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will we end up living here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must find a way out!\NI'm worried about Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Jewel Shards, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For starters, let's talk to\nthe men here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me... What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't the real world.\NDo you realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please... are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!\NWe're in the midst of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are training in here\nto become sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Training to become sages?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:19.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we become as strong as sages,\nwe'll be released from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Master Tokajin will give\nus the Fruit of Longevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he the villain who\nput you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Tokajin rescued us\nfrom hunger and war!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He is our saviour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't speak ill of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... no matter how I look at it,\nit's just a rusty, old sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I know the sword transformed when\nthat young kid hurled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right... I dropped Tetsusaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:15.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being unable to transform into\na demon shows how weak I've gotten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But damn! What a place this is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! My robe of the fire-rat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't waste time in here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I'll just have to\nclaw my way out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! I merely scratched it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only I had Tetsusaiga,\nthis would be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That punk! I'll teach 'im when\NI get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My claws...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! My power is disappearing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel Shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With just one shard, my body\ncan deflect a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this many, my body will be\na metal armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! It's rising!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't' figure something out,\NI'll melt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! What'll I do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can become a sage\ndoing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mastering Sagery requires\nphysical strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I believe spiritual\nprowess is critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't seem to be\nfrom the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mr. Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You seem to be different\nfrom the others here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No... I'm just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was among the vanquished\nand escaped into the valley,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then was captured by Tokajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to train\nto become a sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:37.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once you master even a tiny bit\nof Sagery,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you become fodder for\nthe Tree of the Human-faced Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin talking to the Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tree of Human-faced Fruit!\NIsn't it time yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When will you bear\nthe Fruit of Longevity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not for a long while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need lots and lots more\nsouls of sages!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There aren't that many sages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Silence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just do as I say!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Tree, you are a nuisance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just remove this,\nso you can't talk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}H- Hey! Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll wear it for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, I'll bring you\nsage souls without fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's there?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another vanquished soldier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Train hard, then come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's probably a Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:18:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's slight, but I definitely sense\nthe presence of the Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what an awful sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have heard that unless a man\nrenounces the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and becomes a hermit,\none cannot become a sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:17.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why these men cannot\nbecome sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poormen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're training, only to end up\nas nourishment for the demon tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those men turn deaf ears to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we talk to them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:35.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it'll serve no purpose.\NThere's no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! There {\i1}must{\i0} be a way!\NThere has to be a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha... please be well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!\NI can feel pain now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:59.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I hate being mortal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I get out of here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sheathe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is calling Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga is close by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, I may be saved yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come! Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?! That rusty sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you're prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're that demon kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!\NThis is payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww, that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A Jewel Shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...! You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you... Where'd you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Couldn't possibly be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid! You're the one who'd\nbetter be ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C-Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The power of the Jewel Shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How... How can we get out of here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}By now, Inuyasha is probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, it's no good.\NThere's no exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter where we go,\nthere are walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's either become a sage and get fed\nto the Tree of the Human-faced Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or stay here and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are the only two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:50.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:54.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a place without\ndreams or hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh... if this is a dream,\nlet me awaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:05.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stand this nightmare\nany longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a dream... just a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, pinch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owwee! It's not a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, it's the new moon\nand you've turned into a mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way you can beat\nthat sage with creepy powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:04.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're sacrificing your life\nto save mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! No, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Fateful Night in Togenkyo, Part II"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Daybreak! Hurry!
